      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in breathtaking showroom condition, this vehicle stands as a testament to meticulous ownership and uncompromising care. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, hand-tailored interior, remains in an as-delivered state. This is more than a pre-owned vehicle; it is a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark example that performs with the precision of a new car. For the discerning driver who accepts only the finest, this offering represents the absolute pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48900.0,
